trans-unit.source: Specifies constants that define which mouse button was pressed.
trans-unit.target: Angir konstanter som definerer hvilke museknappen ble brukt.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by many classes, including <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RadioButton>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.UpDownBase>.
trans-unit.target: Denne nummerering brukes av mange klasser, inkludert <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RadioButton>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar>, og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.UpDownBase>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.UpDownBase> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.StatusBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Splitter> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.RadioButton> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGrid> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.AxHost>

trans-unit.source: The left mouse button was pressed.
The middle mouse button was pressed.
The right mouse button was pressed.
With Windows 2000, Microsoft is introducing support for the Microsoft IntelliMouse Explorer, which is a mouse with five buttons.
trans-unit.target: Med Windows 2000 introduserer Microsoft Kundestøtte for Microsoft IntelliMouse Explorer, som er en mus med fem knapper.

trans-unit.source: The two new mouse buttons (XBUTTON1 and XBUTTON2) provide backward/forward navigation.
trans-unit.target: To nye museknappen (XBUTTON1 og XBUTTON2) inneholder bakover/fremover navigasjon.
